:INFO
The Novel That Required More From Me Than I Expected
I first attempted Beloved in college and stopped at page 30. The second \
attempt came five years later and ended around page 80. The third attempt came \
after I had spent a year reading more widely in American history and literature, \
and something in that preparation made the difference. Toni Morrison does not \
explain what she is doing. She trusts you to follow her into the grief of it, \
and the third time I was finally able to follow.

:COUNTER.half
321 Pages
|
