:QUOTE [subtitle:Toni Morrison, quotetype:PLAIN]
124 was spiteful. Full of a baby's venom.

:JOURNEY
Reading Beloved
Section
Impact
- First 50 pages | 3 | Dense and nonlinear
- Middle section | 5 | Weight arrives
- Beloved as presence | 5 | Powerful choice
- Final chapter | 5 | Stays with you | Ends with a command I could not shake for weeks

:NOTE
Reading American history before this novel is not required but it is a gift \
to yourself. The book is more accessible when you already know something of \
the world it enters.

